    "Secondly, the search for related studies was conducted across three databases.",
    "However, to attain more comprehensive results, it is advisable to conduct further research across additional databases.",
    "ConclusionIn conclusion, our systematic review and meta-analysis revealed a substantial and statistically significant improvement in cognitive function through the utilization of virtual reality interventions.",
